"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:7.4.5\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">7.4.5</span> 标题：木拍板（wooden clappers）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：עֵץ, בְּרוֹשׁ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：‘atsey broshim)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:5\">2SA 6:5</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>拍板的形状有扁平状、长圆形、长方形或弧形，可以由木头、象牙或骨头制成。所有板子的一端系在一起，从而能够互相碰击，发出清脆、短促的拍打声。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>许多文化都知道与“木拍板”类似的打击乐器，演奏方法和外观与拍板类似。</p>\n<p>学者对<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:5\">2SA 6:5</a> 中的希伯来文短语<em>‘atseybroshim</em> 有几种解释。这个短语的字面意思是“柏树”或“柏木片”，因此有些学者认为它不是指乐器，而是指人们挥舞柏树枝来表达喜悦之情。还有一些学者将其解作“柏木做的多种乐器”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Italian Common Language Version\">ITCL</abbr> 直译），暗示它是经文所列多种乐器中的一个单独的条目。这个短语也可能是制作清单中后续各种乐器所用的材料；这节经文的后半句可译为：“他们演奏各样木制的乐器：琴、瑟、鼓、拨浪鼓和锣”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 直译）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
